  [Text] President Ilyas al-Hirawi received Phalangist Party 
leader Dr. George Sa'adah yesterday. Sa'adah said al-Hirawi 
briefed him on the reasons prompting the government to postpone 
granting permission to radio stations to broadcast news and 
explained the recent suspension of newscasts. He said: I was 
