settle this issue quickly. 
  Dr. Sa'adah spoke of the possibility of links between the 
bombing of the Sayyidat al-Najat Church in Zuq Mikha'il and the 
Phalangist Party headquarters, expressing his confidence in the 
Lebanese judiciary and urging patience. 

