  [Text] This morning, the brother President leader 
Abu-'Ammar [Yasir 'Arafat] received the U.S. ambassador in Tunis. 
  During the meeting, the brother President leader Abu-'Ammar 
charged his excellency the U.S. ambassador with conveying a 
message to the U.S. Administration in connection with the 
Palestinian stance toward the Israeli replies to the Palestinian 
demands on providing international protection to our Palestinian 
people and implementing Security Council Resolution 904. 
  The recent developments in connection with the Palestinian 
issue and the events currently taking place in the occupied 
Palestinian territories were also discussed during the meeting. 

