<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Receives Phone Call From Christopher </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Receives Phone Call From Christopher </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3103211094 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
31 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3103211094 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] President 'Arafat yesterday evening received a 
telephone call from U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher. 
'Arafat asked Mr. Christopher for the U.S. Administration's 
help in urging Israel to agree on expanding the extent and the 
size of international presence in Hebron and the importance of 
implementing UN Security Council Resolution 904 regarding 
international protection for our people inside the occupied 
Palestinian territories. 

</TEXT>

