<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Fatah Closes Offices in Territories </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fatah Closes Offices in Territories </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0104043894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 1 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0104043894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The PLO's Fatah organization has closed its offices 
in the territories in protest at what it calls the continuing 
massacres of Palestinians. Palestinian sources said the step 
was part of an effort by Yasir 'Arafat to quell Fatah infighting. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

